{"id":334618,"type":3,"name":"LISTEN","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/56/9c/334618_N5Utx.jpg","summary":"夏語遙首張限量官方音樂專輯\r\n這是由 VOICEMITH 主導的夏語遙首張音樂專輯，包括混音和後期母帶後製處理，除了能呈現高品質的聲音。本專輯的製作邀請多人參與，除了詞曲創作者來自台灣、中國大陸、香港，力求多元風格外，也廣邀不同的調聲者，為語遙塑造不同的聲線。同時編曲、混音和後製等幕後人員的付出，也是功不可沒。\r\n\r\n形象設計由繪師 VOFAN 操刀\r\nVOFAN 為台日知名繪師，曾為台灣 Pay Station 設計官方專屬角色「小藍」。本計畫邀請他擔任專輯形象設計者，希望除了好聽的歌曲外，透過 VOFAN 細膩的筆觸，能表現出讓人耳目一些的感覺!","info":"<li><span>作曲: </span>Cire、<a href=\"/person/40186\">纯白</a>P、KIWI、Eric Chou、Packer、許晉嘉、張哲、野良犬P、Kim San</li><li><span>作词: </span>Cire、<a href=\"/person/36410\">雨狸</a>、KIWI、月隱夜色、胡桃、Miliguo、張哲、野良犬P、Kim San</li><li><span>编曲: </span>Cire、<a href=\"/person/40186\">纯白</a>P、KIWI、Onai P、Packer、許晉嘉、Max Jr.、Eric Chou</li><li><span>插图: </span><a href=\"/person/3720\">VOFAN</a></li><li><span>版本特性: </span>Limited Edition</li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2018-06-16</li><li><span>价格: </span>NT$950</li><li><span>艺术家: </span>夏語遙</li><li><span>制作人: </span>VOICEMITH</li>","eps":[{"id":0,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/0","type":0,"sort":0,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":""}],"disc":[{"title":"Disc 1","disc":[{"title":"1 Listen","href":"/ep/1027139"},{"title":"2 詞不達意","href":"/ep/1027140"},{"title":"3 YAO","href":"/ep/1027141"},{"title":"4 檸檬巧克力","href":"/ep/1027142"},{"title":"5 交換禮物","href":"/ep/1027143"},{"title":"6 愛不自由","href":"/ep/1027144"},{"title":"7 返現實","href":"/ep/1027145"},{"title":"8 追花","href":"/ep/1027146"},{"title":"9 下雨天","href":"/ep/1027147"},{"title":"10 下雨天(合唱版)","href":"/ep/1027148"},{"title":"11 Listen(日語版)","href":"/ep/1027149"}]}],"crt":[{"id":33634,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d2/3e/33634_crt_FZfpx.jpg","name":"夏语遥","desc":"主角"}],"staff":[{"id":40186,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/42/7d/40186_prsn_wb8Dq.jpg","name":"纯白","desc":"作曲"},{"id":36410,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f8/eb/36410_prsn_McKD9.jpg","name":"雨狸","desc":"作词"},{"id":3720,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/96/d3/3720_prsn_Kz636.jpg","name":"戴源亨","desc":"插图"}]}